# SpectraUtils

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![NuGet](https://img.shields.io/nuget/v/SpectraUtils.svg)](https://www.nuget.org/packages/SpectraUtils/)
[![.NET 9.0](https://img.shields.io/badge/.NET-9.0-512BD4)](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/)

SpectraUtils is a small but opinionated toolbox I keep using across projects: validation attributes, Turkish-aware name formatting, and a couple of security-focused helpers (password hashing, tokens, OTP codes).

I originally built this package while learning how to publish my first NuGet package. Since then, I’ve kept evolving it as I grew into a solid mid-level developer — with more focus on clean APIs, safety, and real-world usage.

If you know me from YouTube (I’m Oğuzhan Karagüzel and I share C# education content), this repository is basically the “utilities folder” I decided to maintain properly.

## Features

### Security services

- PBKDF2 password hashing (`Pbkdf2PasswordHasher`)
- Base64Url secure token generation (`SecureTokenGenerator`)
- Numeric one-time codes / OTP (`OneTimeCodeGenerator`)
- Password creation helper (`PasswordHelper`)

### Validation attributes

- Minimum age validation for `DateTime` and `DateOnly` (`MinimumAgeAttribute`)
- Turkish National ID validation (`TCIDValidationAttribute`)
- Turkish tax number (VKN) validation (`TurkishTaxNumberValidationAttribute`)
- IBAN validation (`IbanValidationAttribute`)
- Allowed file extensions + max size validation for `IFormFile` and file paths (`AllowedExtensionsAttribute`)

### Extensions & utilities

- String extensions (`IsNullOrEmpty`, `IsNullOrWhiteSpace`, `ReverseSafe`)
- DI registration (`AddSpectraUtils`, `AddSpectraUtilsScoped`)

---

## Targets

- .NET 9 (`net9.0`)

---

## Installation

```bash
dotnet add package SpectraUtils
```

---

## Dependency Injection (recommended)

```csharp
using SpectraUtils.Extensions;

builder.Services.AddSpectraUtils();
// or
builder.Services.AddSpectraUtilsScoped();
```

Then consume the facade:

```csharp
using SpectraUtils;

ISpectraUtil util = serviceProvider.GetRequiredService<ISpectraUtil>();
```

---

## Basic usage

### Name formatting

```csharp
var util = serviceProvider.GetRequiredService<ISpectraUtil>();

string name = util.NameEdit.NameCorrection("oĞuzHan");
string sirName = util.NameEdit.SirNameCorrection("karagüzel");

// "Oğuzhan"
// "KARAGÜZEL"
```

### Password creation

```csharp
var util = serviceProvider.GetRequiredService<ISpectraUtil>();

string password = util.PasswordHelper.CreatePassword(
    passwordLength: 8,
    includeLowercaseLetter: true,
    includeNumber: true,
    includeUppercaseLetter: true,
    includeSpecialCharacter: true);

string standardPassword = util.PasswordHelper.CreateStardartPassword;
```

### Validation attributes

```csharp
using SpectraUtils.Attributes.ValidationAttributes;

public sealed class RegisterRequest
{
    [MinimumAge(18)]
    public DateTime BirthDate { get; set; }

    [TCIDValidation]
    public string Identity { get; set; } = string.Empty;

    [AllowedExtensions(2 * 1024 * 1024, ".jpg", ".jpeg", ".png", ".pdf")]
    public IFormFile? File { get; set; }
}
```

